content.warning: Son ta'n obbyr shoh ry-gheddyn son ymmodee ceadyn er dty phone-mobile, ta mooarane ceadyn ard-risky, shen-y-fa nagh jean ad import ny cur ad er-chea gyn ad dy hoiggal ny risksyn jeh'n margagh ny script.
